							3.8
						</p>
						

						
						

						
						
						

						
						<p><strong>Release Notes</strong></p>
						<div class="cy-app-release-notes">**NOTE:** Do not use this version on **Cytoscape 3.9.x** or below. Use version ``2.0.2`` instead.

- Fixes bug where all clusters were named &quot;Cluster 0&quot;.
- Updates the version of the ``pax-logging-api`` dependency to ``1.11.13`` in order to prevent security warnings related to a _Log4J_ vulnerability issue.</div>
						
						
